+\fIname\fR parameter as in the \fBupdate add\fR command. The \fIttl\fR item is ignored.
+
+.TP
+\fBshow\fR
+
+Displays current content of the update message.
+
+.TP
+\fBsend\fR
+
+Sends the current update message and cleans the list of updates.
+
+.TP
+\fBanswer\fR
+
